Did you know that there are more than 15 ways to say “good luck” in Spanish? But why so many different ways?&nbsp;
Remember, there are 21 Spanish-speaking countries in the world. Each country has its own regional vocabulary and slang. That includes all the ways of wishing people well.&nbsp;
Even if you aren’t superstitious, saying “good luck” is a nice way to show support to your family and friends. You don’t have to know every possible phrase.

